   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for fa\"><tr><td>fa</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\n<h2>Friedreich Ataxia data</h2>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>This data set contains a case-control indicator and twelve\nmicrosatellite markers. An extra unphased individual with the following\ngenotype\n</p>\n<pre>\n 2  7  7  7  1  3  2  2  2  2  6  3\n 3  8 10  8  3  9  3  4  2  2  7  5\n</pre>\n<p>has not been included.\n</p>\n<p>The inter-marker distances (Morgan) are as follows,\n</p>\n<p>0.03, 0.065, 0.00125, 0.00125, 0.00125, 0.00125, \n0.00125, 0.00125, 0.00125, 0.00125, 0.045\n</p>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<pre>data(fa)</pre>\n<h3>Format</h3>\n<p>A data frame containing 127 rows and 13 columns</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p>Liu JS, Sabatti C, Teng J, Keats BJB, Risch N (2001). \nBayesian analysis of haplotypes for linkage disequilibrium mapping\nGenome Research 11:1716-1724</p>\n",
